It'd be nice to have a symbolic constant denoting EL1t.

> +	msr	spsr_el2, x4
> +	adrp	x4, 1f
> +	add	x4, x4, :lo12:1f
> +	msr	elr_el2, x4
> +	isb

You can drop this ISB, as the following ERET has the same context
synchronisation properties.

> +	eret
>  1:
>  	/* zero BSS */
>  	adrp	x4, bss
> @@ -186,6 +197,18 @@ get_mmu_off:
